vote.title: A public hearing to receive comments regarding a proposal to consider a request to change the name of Village Fair Place, between Village Fair Drive and Ledbetter Drive, to “Pastor Pryor Drive” and an ordinance granting the name change - NC201-002 - Financing: New street blades to be prepared and paid for by the City of Dallas (see Fiscal Information for potential future costs)
